            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 6962,
            "LocalizeKR": "어떤 척박한 곳이라도\n강하게 뿌리내리는,\n끈질김이…….",
